Perfect security
------------
Nette uses revolutionary technology that eliminates security holes and their misuse, such as XSS((Cross-site scripting)), CSRF((Cross-site request forgery)), session hijacking, session fixation, etc. [Want to know more? | features/security]


[* lamplight1-48x48.png .[icon] *]

Debugging tools
----------
Possesses unmatched [debug tools | http://zdrojak.root.cz/clanky/nette-framework-odvsivujeme/], which will help you discover all bugs in timely fashion.


[* time-48x48.png .[icon] *]

Excels in performance
---------------
According to [an independent test | http://www.root.cz/clanky/velky-test-php-frameworku-zend-nette-php-a-ror/] Nette Framework is one of the fastest frameworks ever.


[* discussion-48x48.png .[icon] *]

